social_posts.post_text: Hit ‘em hard and low. Big ❤️ for my team @rebellionrugby. 📸: @andrewthillphoto
#ocean meets land 🌊 #goldenhour #drone session in #florida on the #beach

Gotta make the most of it! Adventure recap time with my friends. Went to Catalina Island with Nick and Amanda.  Went scuba diving and rented kayaks. Camped on the beach and had piña coladas in the rain! Chilled with 2 giant sea bass, lots of jelly fish, seals and a sea slug. Felt like the little mermaid. 🧜‍♀️🐟
What we think about the fit for #whalerock? Thanks to my friends and followers for making this all possible #cringe #influencer #fame #jaminthevan

Since when did growing up mean giving up what makes you happy 🌊🏄 If you invite me to surf, just know I’m gonna show up with my boogie board. I’ll catch the same waves, but leave the bad vibes at home and share the ocean! #nevergrowup #surfing #boogieboarding
